propertyObj.key: SAP S4HANA Cloud Price Condition Code
propertyObj.description:
This is the condition type that is used to find all product prices in S4HANA Cloud  

 

Example of a valid value: ZPR0

The Distribution Channel 

 

Example of a valid value: 10

This is the code of the Sales Organization  

 

Example of a valid value: 3810

propertyObj.key: SAP S4HANA Cloud Discount Condition Code
propertyObj.description:
This is the condition type that is used to find all product discounts in S4HANA Cloud  
 

Example of a valid value: ZM01

Indicates whether logging of Exceptions, as attachments, is enabled.  

  

Default Value: true  

Valid values: true/false

Specify the SAP S/4HANA Cloud API Base URL  

  

Example:
https://xxxxxxx-api.s4hana.cloud.sap/

The type of proxy you want to use for establishing connection with the OData V2 service.

Default value: Internet
Authentication method that you want to use for connecting to the OData V2 service.
Specify the name/alias of the deployed User Credentials Security Material that holds the username and password used to authenticate with SAP S/4HANA Cloud

Keep this option selected (default setting). It ensures that your integration flow is protected against Cross-Site-Request-Forgery, a kind of attack where a malicious party can perform harmful actions by masquerading as the logged in user.

The option is enabled by default. This option enables the reuse of connection objects from the internal connection pool, which in turn improves the network turnaround time for multiple communications to a same end point.

propertyObj.key: Big Commerce Can Use Discount in Conjunction with Other Discounts
propertyObj.description:
Specify whether product discounts can be used together with other product discounts in the shopping cart. 

 

Default value: false 

 

Valid values: true/false

Your BigCommerce base URL. The store hash part can be extracted from the BigCommerce dashboard URL: https://store-XXXXXX.mybigcommerce.com/manage/dashboard 

  

Example of a valid value:  

https://api.bigcommerce.com/stores/abcdef1234
Specify the name of the deployed Secure Parameter that holds the access token used to authorize requests to BigCommerce

propertyObj.key: BigCommerce Attach Error Details on Failure
propertyObj.description:
If selected, any errors encountered by the adapter will be output in a separate text attachment 

 

Default value: True

Specify the accepted response headers. Use a pipe “|”-separated list. Using “*” will accept all response headers 

Default value: *

Configure the session handling scope for HTTP based endpoints
Options:
None - Switched off
On Exchange - Each exchange corresponds to a single session
On Integration Flow - Only one session will be used across the whole integration flow
It is visible only when On-Premise is selected for Proxy type. Used to connect Cloud SAP Connector with your account.
It is visible only when Client Certificate is selected for Authentication. Enter the alias of the deployed private key.

propertyObj.key: Replicate Single Product Price and Discount Flow
propertyObj.description:
Link to the Replicate Single Product Price and Discounts Integration Flow.  
  

Example for Valid Values:  

/Replicate_Single_Product_Price_and_Discounts_BigCommerce
